'''One: the Body, Mind & Spirit channel''' (often referred to only as '''One''') is a [[Canada|Canadian]] [[English language]] [[Category 1 channels (Canada)|category 1]] [[digital cable]] [[specialty channel]]. It provides progressive programming from Canada and around the world on [[natural health]], [[personal growth]], new ideas, holistic lifestyle and intriguing possibilities.  The channel is owned by [[S-VOX]] with minority interests held by CW Media (a division of [[Canwest]] and [[GS Capital Partners]]), [[RNC Media]] and [[Renewal Partners Company]].

